Build all the child projects first

$ sudo docker run --network="host" -it --env-file .env -v ${PWD}:/camunda --entrypoint=bash workflow

$ cd IdentityService/
$ ./gradlew build

$ cd ../TaskListener/
$ ./gradlew build

$ cd ../ProcessEngine/
$ ./gradlew build
$ mkdir -p dist
$ cp build/libs/processengine_plugin-1.0.jar dist/processengine_plugin.jar 

To build the docker container
$ docker build -t workflow .

copy the .env.sample to .env and update the db host, user and password values

To run the docker container in foreground
$ docker run --network="host" -it --env-file .env workflow

To run the docker container in background
$ docker run --network="host" -d --env-file .env --rm --name wf_1 workflow

To stop the docker when running in background mode
$ docker stop wf_1
